---
title: Squash Ravioli in Sun-Dried Tomato Sauce with Peppers and Basil
description: Zesty sun-dried tomato pesto is the perfect pair for hearty tomato sauce. We've given this combo a savoury boost by adding sautéed peppers and onions. All that flavour comes to life over tender, sweet squash ravioli. Don't forget the final sprinkle of basil and Parm!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/raviolis-a-la-courge-dans-une-sauce-de-tomates-sechees-4d9aae6c.jpg
